{"tid":2107562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個熱血公民 咁既新西陣容真係得啖笑","createTime":"2020-07-14T03:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T10:02:44.000Z","uid":3747,"like":47,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b6144e7581b3a7684cea7b6e4d65bb9683d82133","tid":2107562,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"講真咁同直接宣佈鄭松泰連任有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班熱狗 totally no mood to 捱夜開票 <br />\n嗱,我又分析下 首先珠海的,唔好玩啦 左膠野，騎住穩陣<br />\n<br />\n黃子悅,,如果係黃子華就有可觀性(順便可以報上次去老燒節目ga仇)(不過算啦,入到議會又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依條女..熱半力夠WIN,又騎住<br />\n<br />\n最後個d,我連名都唔記得 我地出排第二去論壇練下is ok,又騎住<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 法子,兆健,王姑娘,皇后 加上關鍵王洋達.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n大勝就一定..係睇下破唔破到十萬飛.咁一面倒ga選舉,我冇興趣,大家10月見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手熱血公民 ...is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"314af033cc4528f9ed47fdc50368c02229628b63","tid":2107562,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"法子有望成為票王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009aa1ae04365dc6bf3a96c8f20a8b013002641e","tid":2107562,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51395457be651af0330b7b40a5c952af186bb0c8","tid":2107562,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"皇后同王姑娘咩人來"},{"pid":"d13645ae70e82ddb9ce9da2b7d23ae2dc9717121","tid":2107562,"uid":20908,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"on9熱狗"},{"pid":"cabb1229e9a7a49938f725542d1c71af01ca80e1","tid":2107562,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51395457be651af0330b7b40a5c952af186bb0c8","tid":2107562,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"皇后同